ecanismo → inflamacion/edema → isquemia → degeneracion Walleriana","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"188","text":"Factores de\\Nriesgo en AM","guid":"VIjpCStF70DcOcf7sXZm9Q","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"Edad → predictor CRITICO de mal pronostico (p<0.001)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"Hipertension arterial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"192","text":"Diabetes mellitus (OR 2.4)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"192","text":"Depresion (OR 2.05)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"197","parent":"188","text":"Pronostico\\Ngeneral","guid":"ruA91xCtcxmpky-O7prnsA","children":[{"id":"198","parent":"197","text":"70-85% recuperacion completa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"197","text":"13% recuperacion parcial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"197","text":"16% paralisis persistente con sincinesias","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"188","text":"Factores\\Npronosticos","guid":"f42SF77yoYvJrVx9L7ixvg","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"Edad joven → mejor recuperacion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"203","parent":"201","text":"Grado House-Brackmann inicial (III-IV > V-VI)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"201","text":"Menor reduccion de amplitud en electroneurografia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"201","text":"Ausencia de HTA/DM","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"206","parent":"188","text":"Tiempo medio de recuperacion a H-B I → 6 semanas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"188","text":"Paralisis severa (H-B V-VI) → MAYOR riesgo de sincinesias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"188","text":"Manejo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"209","parent":"208","text":"Corticoides → prednisona\\N1mg/kg/dia x 7 dias con taper","guid":"jKxHUsVQFczX7I20pYm22w","children":[{"id":"210","parent":"209","text":"NNT ~6 para recuperacion completa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"209","t